– Dialogues again sorted by last update

For this update we focused on improving the app's stability and correcting a few bugs.

We know, some of our users might have experiences problems with our messenger. That's why we decided to rewrite it from ground up.
Now our chat is much faster, it's beautifully designed and, of course, doesn't have any bugs.

If you like this update, please write a review in AppStore, this will help us a lot.
You can also send us bug reports through feedback form in the app (Settings -> Leave feedback).

A gift is a best way to start a conversation, be it with your mom or with a potential girlfriend. It attracts a lot of attention. We added gifts shortcut right inside our messenger, so now you're one tap away from making other users much happier.

If you like this update, please write a review in AppStore, this will help us a lot.

You can also send us bug reports through feedback form in the app (Settings -> Leave feedback).

Gifts! Do you know, that you can buy a gift to a young stellar woman and start a conversation with her right away? That is true! Try it out! Ladies, it works perfectly with men as well :wink:
And, since most of you don’t know that, we now have a simple beautiful button on each user’s profile, that informs you about it.

By the way, as usual, we fix small insignificant bugs, so finding your true love is even more simple and fun.
